        <div class="card-num">App 04</div>
        <h3 class="card-title">Event Info Page</h3>
        <p class="card-tagline">Where to park. Which hotel. What to wear. One link that answers every text you'd get five times.</p>
        <p class="card-fork">Multiple events across the weekend? Clone one per day.</p>
